-   <xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException>  
  
-   <xref:System.IO.FileLoadException>  
  
-   <xref:System.IO.PathTooLongException>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="645af-104">必要に応じて、IOException の代わりにこれらの型を使用します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="645af-104">Where appropriate, use these types instead of IOException.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="645af-105"><xref:System.IO.IOException> 値は 0x80131620 HRESULT COR_E_IO を使用します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="645af-105"><xref:System.IO.IOException> uses the HRESULT COR_E_IO which has the value 0x80131620.</span></span>  
  
   
  
